    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Puter.js App Template</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">A serverless, cloud-powered application template</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <p>
                    This is a template for building single-file Puter.js applications 
                    that can be deployed to GitHub Pages with zero backend infrastructure.
